articles.title: GTA 6 Release Date Narrowed to Fall 2025 Amid Questions about Delays - IGN
articles.description: Take-Two Interactive's latest earnings revealed that GTA 6 will release in fall 2025, with CEO Strauss Zelnick telling IGN that he is "highly confident" that it will meet its updated release date.
articles.content: Take-Two Interactive is doubling down Grand Theft Auto VI's release date, saying the long-awaited sequel will be out fall 2025 despite rumors of a possible delay into 2026. Take-Two announced GTA 6's… [+1647 chars]
